<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَسَهْواً: فَـ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- إِنْ ذَكَرَ قَرِيباً أَتَمَّهَا وَسَجَدَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَإِنْ أَحْدَثَ،<span class="c5"> أَوْ قَهْقَهَ:</span> بَطَلَتْ؛ كَفِعْلِهِمَا فِي صُلْبِهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- نَفَخَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- أَوِ انْتَحَبَ <span class="c2">(١)</span> لَا مِنْ خَشْيَةِ اللهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- أَوْ تَنَحْنَحَ بِلَا حَاجَةٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">فَبَانَ حَرْفَانِ:</span> بَطَلَتْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَمَنْ تَرَكَ رُكْناً غَيْرَ التَّحْرِيمَةِ،<span class="c5"> فَذَكَرَهُ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span class="c5"> بَعْدَ شُرُوعِهِ فِي قِرَاءَةِ رَكْعَةٍ أُخْرَى:</span> بَطَلَتِ المَتْرُوكُ مِنْهَا، وَصَارَتِ الَّتِي شَرَعَ فِي قِرَاءَتِهَا مَكَانَهَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَقَبْلَهُ:</span> يَعُودُ فَيَأْتِي بِهِ وَبِمَا بَعْدَهُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَبَعْدَ سَلَامٍ:</span> فَكَتَرْكِ رَكْعَةٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ نَهَضَ عَنْ تَشَهُّدٍ أَوَّلَ نَاسِياً:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- لَزِمَ رُجُوعُهُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) النحيب: رفع الصوت بالبكاء. ينظر: المطلع ص ١١٤.</p> </div>